OL,3,CChancellor defends UK Government
OL,4,Cfunding for Wales
OL,6,FChancellor of the Exchequer Rachel
OL,7,FReeves has defended the level of the
OL,8,FUK Government's spending in Wales
OL,9,Fduring a visit to a coal tip
OL,10,Fremediation site near Port Talbot.
OL,12,FMeeting Welsh Finance Secretary Mark
OL,13,FDrakeford MS, she pointed to #118m
OL,14,Fallocated in the recent Spending
OL,15,FReview over three years to improve
OL,16,Fdisused coal tips across Wales.
