OL,3,CChancellor defends UK Government
OL,4,Cfunding for Wales
OL,6,F"The whole of the United Kingdom has
OL,7,Fbenefited from coal in Wales and
OL,8,Ftherefore it's right that the UK make
OL,9,Fsure that these communities are now
OL,10,Fsafe" she said.
OL,12,FThe visit comes just one day after
OL,13,FEluned Morgan completed one year as
OL,14,FFirst Minister, during which time she
OL,15,Finsisted she would "call out" Labour
OL,16,FMPs in Westminster if they "get it
OL,17,Fwrong for Wales".
