OL,3,CChancellor defends UK Government
OL,4,Cfunding for Wales
OL,6,FReeves said she continues to work
OL,7,Fclosely with the First Minister and
OL,8,Fsaid the partnership has provided
OL,9,Fmoney for rail improvements in North
OL,10,Fand South Wales, "the biggest
OL,11,Fsettlement since devolution", and a
OL,12,Ffall in NHS waiting lists in England
OL,13,Fand Wales.
OL,15,FShe also defended the UK Government's
OL,16,Fcontroversial rise in employers'
OL,17,FNational Insurance contributions.
